{"id":260576,"type":6,"name":"天涯明月刀","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/4c/8c/260576_PTOU7.jpg","summary":"        傅红雪（狄龙 饰）和燕南飞（罗烈 饰）在比武过程中遭遇顶尖杀手的袭击，他们躲过接二连三的暗算，终于从明月心（恬妮 饰）的口中知晓了幕后黑手的真实身份，那就是妄图称霸武林的公子羽。为了对抗公子羽，二人结伴前往孔雀山庄去取兵器谱排名第一的孔雀翎，而得知消息的公子羽也再度派出杀手截杀二人。绝世兵器给孔雀山庄带来了血腥灾难。围绕孔雀翎和第一高手的名头，不断有人丧失性命。而在这一过程中，傅红雪也发现了公子羽背后的秘密…… ","info":"<li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/17449\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">楚原</a></li><li><span>编剧: </span><a href=\"/person/33327\">倪匡</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/33302\">谷峰</a>、<a href=\"/person/16738\">狄龍</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>天涯，明月，刀</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>The Magic Blade</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>语言: </span>粤语</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0075329</li><li><span>上映日期: </span>1976-07-10(香港)</li><li><span>片长: </span>97分钟</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"邵氏","count":1},{"name":"武侠","count":1},{"name":"电影","count":1},{"name":"小说改","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":827524,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/827524","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":16836,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bb/c3/16836_prsn_qneSX.jpg","name":"古龙","desc":"原作"},{"id":17449,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/00/6d/17449_prsn_qVScc.jpg","name":"楚原","desc":"导演"},{"id":33327,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/10/66/33327_prsn_25GZe.jpg","name":"倪匡","desc":"编剧"},{"id":33302,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/44/6d/33302_prsn_0ww8F.jpg","name":"谷峰","desc":"主演"},{"id":16738,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/db/1e/16738_prsn_43Z8P.jpg","name":"狄龙","desc":"主演"}],"relations":[{"id":124127,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1e/6f/124127_S1G3w.jpg","title":"天涯·明月·刀","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/124127"}]}